External Knowledge:
A "composite rating" represents the weighted average of evaluation criteria ratings (Poor = 1, Competent = 2, Good = 3, Excellent = 4); 
An "Altmetric score" is a measure of the online attention and impact of a research contribution; 
Citation counts are a measure of how many times a research contribution has been cited by other researchers.
